data.title: Dharma Chakram Cast Members List
data.meta_description: List of actors and actresses who star in Dharma Chakram (list of Dharma Chakram cast members).

Daggubati Venkatesh (born 13 December 1960) is an Indian film actor known for his works predominantly in Telugu cinema. Venkatesh debuted with the 1986 film Kaliyuga Pandavulu for which he won his first Nandi Award. In a career spanning over 30 years ... more »

Ramya Krishnan (born 15 September 1970) is an Indian film actress. She has acted in over 260 films in five languages: Telugu, Tamil, Kannada, Malayalam and Hindi. Ramya has won four Filmfare Awards, three Nandi Awards and a Tamil Nadu State Film Award ... more »
